LLM_response_editer_en:
According to the status of the existing screen image, we can see a blank text editor window. To enter text in the text editor, we can do the following:```json
[
    {"action_type": "KeyboardAction", "keyboard_action_type": "text", "keyboard_text": "Hello, world!"},
    {"action_type": "KeyboardAction", "keyboard_action_type": "press", "keyboard_key": "Return"}
]
```This will enter "Hello, world!" in the text editor and press Enter to save the text in the text editor.
